\begin_layout Subsection
I: Strategy Questions
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Strategy questions include asking what a company’s strategy is or how to
 design a strategy.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It’s important to think about a product’s strategy at two levels: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Micro: What is the business model for the product? What steps is the company
 pursuing to succeed on that model? Will customers want it? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Macro: How does this product fit into the greater vision of the company?
 Will it open up new opportunities? Does it secure an existing market?
\end_layout

